            <item>
    <title>Version 0.3.77</title>
    <description><![CDATA[<h2>What&#x27;s New</h2>

<h3>Browser Extension Testing (87 Playwright tests)</h3>
<li>Full Chromium test suite: lifecycle, tab/nav events, content script interactions (click, input, scroll, selection, reading sessions), URL policy, dashboard UI, video tracking, queue management, sendToHost fallback, browsing trees, settings persistence, delivery pipeline e2e</li>
<li>Safari-mode test suite: loads extension with Safari feature flags in Chromium to verify queue cap (50), disabled APIs, <code>delivery.source = &quot;safariExtension&quot;</code></li>
<li>Runs headless via <code>--headless=new</code></li>

<h3>Browser Extension</h3>
<li><code>sendToHost</code> abstraction for Safari/Chromium parity — falls back to <code>chrome.storage.local</code> when iOS Safari&#x27;s service worker is suspended</li>

<h3>iOS Location Tracking</h3>
<li><b>Location state log table</b> — records every GPS decision (motion debounce, GPS start/stop, span open/close, system pause/resume, auth changes) for debugging geo gaps</li>
<li>Syncs to Mac for remote analysis via MCP</li>]]></description>
